<Game>
	<Name>Kidou Gekidan Haro Ichiza Haro no Puyo Puyo (Japan)</Name>
	<plot>A Puyo Puyo sequel featuring the cast and setting from the Gundam sci-fi series. The game plays exactly the same as the classic Puyo Puyo: you select a character and battle everyone else in the game in Puyo duels, in which each player must align and arrange in colors the falling "puyos" in order to clear them off your screen and avoid flooding your play area, and at the same time sending "garbage" puyos to the opposing player.As mentioned, all characters in the game are SD-versions of Gundam characters, and the puyos themselves have been replaced by the haro capsules featured in the series. Features single player story and arcade modes as well as a Vs 2-player mode.</plot>
